This rule provides standards for frontend components:
Always use Tailwind and shadcn/ui for styling
Follow component naming conventions
Props interface at top. Example UserPageProps
Component as named export
use arrow functions for functions and components
use snake_case for object keys,interfaces
use camelCase for function names, functionparameters,variable names and hooks
use PascalCase for component names
use kebab-case for file names

Folder structure

- features/

  - user/
    - hooks/use-user.ts
    - services/user.service.ts
    - interfaces/user.interface.ts
    - utils/user.utils.ts

- pages/
  - user/
    - hooks/use-user.ts
    - components/
      - user-card.tsx
      - user-list.tsx
      - user-form.tsx
    - pages/
      - user-page.tsx
      - user-list-page.tsx
- services/
- interfaces/
- utils/
- hooks/
- stores/
- routes/
